{"tid":542812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[如果戰事炸彈係德國製造]軍火專家早上7時30分拆彈 道路仍封閉","createTime":"2018-01-27T23:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T23:56:11.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc28488637455b7bea7745900f76917b83b37f46","tid":542812,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T23:56:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/realtime/breaking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking&d=a0EL2TqwfpJ7CvUbxbS21viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=36c0e0f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking&h=3e5520f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/realtime/breaking</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【06:45】警方表示，早上7時30分進行拆彈<br />\n【06:00】警方爆炸品處理課仍未成功拆除炮彈<br />\n<br />\n灣仔沙中綫地盤昨晨發現二戰炮彈，警方封閉灣仔北一帶道路(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2BwrCDE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2BwrCDE&d=a0EL2TqwfpJ7CvUbxbS21viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7649eadb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2BwrCDE</a>)，爆炸品處理課專家通宵處理。為防炮彈不幸爆炸，警方昨晚已在炮彈旁邊堆積沙包，然後處理炸彈，初時估計2小時內才完成拆彈。<br />\n但事件發生了接近一日，至早上6時許軍火專家仍未完成拆彈工序。附近道路依然封閉。<br />\n警方爆炸品處理課高級炸彈處理主任周錫健表示，由於引爆管有損壞，致炸彈狀態不穩定，移動時會有危險。爆炸處理課人員選擇以鑽孔方式，在彈殼上鑽兩個小孔，再以熱力最高只達280&deg;C的特別炸藥燃燒。<br />\n另外，民政事務總署開放灣仔活動中心，供有需要人士前去暫住，由於封路有入住附近酒店人士未能返回酒店。至早上7時，活動中心有4男、10女及6名小童入住，全部是酒店住客。<br />\n<br />\n真係咁多年都無好似　ｒａｍｂｏ　５　咁爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b4A_oMlLL4U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db4A_oMlLL4U&d=a0EL2TqwfpJ7CvUbxbS21viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=59774704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b4A_oMlLL4U</a>"}]}